WEBVTT

00:02.103 --> 00:06.540
* [ Rock ]
[ Children Shouting ]

00:06.574 --> 00:10.678
[ Shutters Clicking ]

00:13.081 --> 00:16.384
MISTER!
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

00:16.417 --> 00:18.519
KITES.

00:20.554 --> 00:24.058
IT MEANS A NEW
DRUG SHIPMENT IS IN.

00:28.762 --> 00:33.567
[ Grey ] I SEE THE KITES.
I DON'T SEE ANY EVIDENCE
OF A DOWNED PLANE.

00:33.601 --> 00:35.603
[ Jonas ]
KEEP LOOKING.

00:35.636 --> 00:38.539
NO-MAN'S LAND.

00:38.572 --> 00:40.474
- MAN, WOMAN OR CHILD.
- [ Shutter Clicks ]

00:59.260 --> 01:01.195
THIS AIN'T A CHRISTENING.

01:01.229 --> 01:03.631
PUT THE CAMERAS DOWN.

01:07.901 --> 01:10.771
[ Children Laughing, Shouting ]

01:13.974 --> 01:15.576
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

01:24.952 --> 01:27.255
- [ Coins Clatter ]
- NO! NO!

01:27.288 --> 01:30.958
- EASY.
- [ Woman Begging ]

01:30.991 --> 01:33.161
[ Gunshot ]

01:33.194 --> 01:36.597
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

01:40.834 --> 01:43.571
[ Gunshots ]
[ Woman Crying ]

01:43.604 --> 01:45.373
[ Gunshot ]

01:49.477 --> 01:51.845
SWEET JESUS.

01:54.848 --> 01:57.218
NOT OUR BUSINESS.

02:23.877 --> 02:27.147
[ Donkey Brays ]

02:30.083 --> 02:34.355
[ Speaks Portuguese ]

02:35.823 --> 02:39.693
[ Speaks Portuguese ]

02:39.727 --> 02:43.531
YES. I WILL.

02:43.564 --> 02:46.567
- YOU SPEAK ENGLISH.
- WHO ARE YOU?

02:46.600 --> 02:48.636
FELLOW WITH SOME MONEY.

02:48.669 --> 02:51.339
YOU PAY ME,
I ANSWER ONE QUESTION.

02:51.372 --> 02:54.475
OKAY.

02:54.508 --> 02:56.977
WHERE'D YOU LEARN ENGLISH?

02:57.010 --> 03:00.047
MY MOTHER CLEANED
THE HOUSE OF AMERICAN IN RIO.

03:00.080 --> 03:03.083
WHERE'S YOUR MOTHER NOW?
DEAD.

03:04.385 --> 03:07.221
THAT MAN OVER THERE--

03:07.255 --> 03:08.922
OH!

03:11.692 --> 03:13.661
I WANT TO TAKE
A PICTURE OF AN AIRPLANE.

03:13.694 --> 03:17.398
YOU TAKE ME TO THIS PLANE,
I GIVE YOU MORE MONEY.

03:17.431 --> 03:21.201
I'LL TAKE YOU TO THE AIRPORT.
NO. I DON'T WANT TO
SEE THAT KIND OF PLANE.

03:21.235 --> 03:23.136
I WANT TO SEE THE PLANE
WHERE YOU GOT THIS.

03:24.438 --> 03:26.607
I BOUGHT IT.
[ Scoffs ]

03:26.640 --> 03:28.842
IN THE STREET.

03:28.876 --> 03:31.479
IF I WAS YOU, MONEY I HAD,
I'D BUY SOME FOOD.

03:33.481 --> 03:35.749
WHERE'D YOU GET
THE HEADSET?

03:39.887 --> 03:42.723
[ Shutter Clicks ]

03:42.756 --> 03:44.858
I DON'T WANT TO GIVE THIS PHOTO
TO THE POLICEMAN NOW, WOULD I?

03:44.892 --> 03:47.861
LET HIM SEE HOW COZY YOU ARE
WITH THE AMERICANS.

03:47.895 --> 03:50.331
[ Donkey Brays ]

04:02.009 --> 04:04.978
[ Flies Buzzing ]
DRUG ERADICATION PLANE.

04:05.012 --> 04:07.147
MUST HAVE BEEN
SPRAYING FOR COCA.

04:08.015 --> 04:10.518
[ Buzzing Continues ]

04:13.321 --> 04:17.491
[ Exhales ]
ALL RIGHT, WHAT ELSE
DID YOU TAKE?

04:17.525 --> 04:21.595
I DON'T CALL THIS NOTHIN'.
I DIDN'T GET THAT HERE.

04:21.629 --> 04:23.731
THAT'S THE LAST LIE
I WANT TO HEAR FROM YOU.

04:23.764 --> 04:26.800
OR I'M GONNA MESS YOU UP
REAL BAD AND TAKE BACK
ALL THAT MONEY.

04:36.544 --> 04:39.780
LET HIM GO.

04:39.813 --> 04:42.282
[ Sighs ]

04:50.624 --> 04:53.093
YOU WANT TO LOOK AT THIS.
ADOLPHO SHOT HIM DOWN.

04:53.126 --> 04:56.864
SURFACE-TO-AIR MISSILE.
HE WAS BRAGGING
HE HAD SAMs.

04:56.897 --> 05:00.768
WELL, I GUESS HE DOES.

05:00.801 --> 05:03.804
QUESTION IS WHAT HE PLANS
TO DO WITH THEM.

05:09.577 --> 05:11.812
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

05:11.845 --> 05:14.181
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

05:14.214 --> 05:16.384
* HERE WE GO
ON THE ROAD *

05:16.417 --> 05:18.786
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

05:18.819 --> 05:20.888
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

05:20.921 --> 05:23.824
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

05:34.435 --> 05:38.038
YOU HAVEN'T
KNOWN HER THAT LONG.
MARRIAGE IS A SERIOUS THING.

05:38.071 --> 05:41.509
JONAS SAID I SHOULD GET YOUR
ADVICE ON THE SUBJECT.
HAVE YOU MET HER FAMILY?

05:41.542 --> 05:44.412
NO. I'M ABOUT TO.
THAT'LL TELL YOU A LOT.

05:44.445 --> 05:46.614
I'M THINKING OF
PROPOSING TO HER,
NOT HER FAMILY.

05:48.215 --> 05:50.484
YOU ARE YOUNG, AREN'T YOU?

05:50.518 --> 05:53.253
SHE THINKS I'M A CLERK
IN THE 303rd.

05:53.286 --> 05:55.923
- WHAT'S YOUR QUESTION?
- WHEN DO I TELL HER
WHAT I DO FOR REAL?

05:55.956 --> 05:58.325
- THAT'S NOT YOUR JOB.
- IT'S NOT?

05:58.358 --> 06:02.362
WHEN YOU DECIDE TO MAKE HER
YOUR FAMILY, YOU'LL BRING HER
TO US WOMEN.

06:02.396 --> 06:07.100
WE'LL TELL HER
WHAT SHE NEEDS TO KNOW. SEE?

06:07.134 --> 06:09.703
YOU'VE JUST LEARNED
SOMETHING NEW.

06:14.575 --> 06:17.578
SIXTEEN-YEAR-OLD BOY COME AND
TAKE MY DAUGHTER TO A MOVIE...

06:17.611 --> 06:20.280
WEARING A SHIRT THAT READS
"STAMP OUT VIRGINITY"?

06:20.313 --> 06:22.349
HUH!
CAN YOU IMAGINE?

06:22.382 --> 06:24.952
YOU REMEMBER THAT, CELESTE?

06:24.985 --> 06:29.356
BIG DECISION AT THAT POINT--
KILL OR JUST MAIM?

06:29.389 --> 06:33.126
I BEAT THAT BOY DOWN THE STREET,
PAST THE CHURCH
AND THE POLICE STATION.

06:33.160 --> 06:36.196
BEAT HIM IN HIS MAMA'S KITCHEN.
LET HIM LIVE,
SO HE COULD REMEMBER.

06:36.229 --> 06:39.232
- DEAR GOD.
- SEE? I DIDN'T REALLY LIKE
THAT BOY ANYHOW.

06:39.266 --> 06:42.102
I JUST BROUGHT HIM HOME TO PUT
A BURR UNDER HIS SADDLE.

06:43.671 --> 06:46.073
LET ME ASK YOU A QUESTION HERE,
HECTOR.

06:46.106 --> 06:48.942
- SIR?
- YOU LOOK HEALTHY ENOUGH.
YOU GOT ALL 10 FINGERS?

06:48.976 --> 06:51.244
YES, SIR.
YOU KNOW HOW TO
SQUEEZE A TRIGGER?

06:51.278 --> 06:53.213
I HAD BASIC TRAINING.

06:53.246 --> 06:56.617
- DO YOU ENJOY THE MILITARY?
- YES, SIR, I DO.

06:56.650 --> 06:59.386
THEN TELL ME HOW
A YOUNG, HEALTHY MAN LIKE YOU...

06:59.419 --> 07:02.956
CAN LOOK AT HISSELF IN A MIRROR
WORKING IN AN OFFICE
WITH A BUNCH OF SKIRTS.

07:02.990 --> 07:07.127
- DADDY!
- IT'S A FAIR QUESTION.
I WANT TO HEAR HIS ANSWER.

07:07.160 --> 07:10.263
SIR, I'M GOOD AT WHAT I DO,
AND IT NEEDS DOING.

07:10.297 --> 07:14.602
- MANAGING LOGISTICS REQUIRES--
- A GENTLE TEMPERAMENT
AND A SORE ASS.

07:14.635 --> 07:16.604
[ Beeping ]

07:16.637 --> 07:18.639
EXCUSE ME.

07:20.974 --> 07:23.410
I APOLOGIZE.
I HAVE TO GO.

07:23.443 --> 07:25.979
ARE THERE SOME PAPERS
IN SERIOUS NEED OF PUSHING?

07:31.652 --> 07:34.321
NONE BUT THE BRAVE
DESERVE THE FAIR.

07:34.354 --> 07:36.690
YOU EVER HEAR THAT, SON?

07:36.724 --> 07:39.627
I'M NOT TRYING
TO HURT YOUR FEELINGS.

07:39.660 --> 07:41.962
BUT MY DAUGHTER IS
NO CONSOLATION PRIZE.

07:41.995 --> 07:44.765
I AGREE, SIR.

07:44.798 --> 07:47.501
WELL, IT SPEAKS WELL
OF YOU THAT YOU DO.

07:47.535 --> 07:50.504
I HAVE TO REPORT TO WORK.

07:51.705 --> 07:54.474
THANK YOU FOR
THE HOSPITALITY, MA'AM.

07:54.508 --> 07:57.377
IT WAS A PLEASURE
TO MEET YOU, HECTOR.

07:57.410 --> 08:00.380
I'LL WALK YOU OUT.

08:04.484 --> 08:06.486
JUST POP THE QUESTION.
IT'S ALL YOU CAN DO.

08:06.520 --> 08:08.856
IT'S A CONTRACT YOU SIGN FIRST.

08:08.889 --> 08:10.858
THEN IT'S THE WOMAN'S CHOICE.

08:10.891 --> 08:12.860
WHO'S GETTING MARRIED?

08:12.893 --> 08:14.862
COULD BE, COLONEL.

08:14.895 --> 08:16.830
WELL, JUST NOT TODAY.

08:16.864 --> 08:20.801
THIS HERE ON THE RIGHT
IS RICARDO RUIZ.

08:20.834 --> 08:24.237
I HEARD RUIZ WAS KILLED
IN A CAR ACCIDENT
IN BELIZE LAST WEEK.

08:24.271 --> 08:28.008
GOOD THING THAT'S WHAT YOU
HEARD, BECAUSE HE'S ALIVE AND
WELL AND IN OUR BRIG ON BASE...

08:28.041 --> 08:30.510
TELLING US ALL ABOUT HIS
FRIENDS AROUND THE GLOBE.
NICE.

08:30.544 --> 08:34.715
ONCE SUCH AMIGO IS THIS MAN,
ADOLPHO JIMENEZ,
BRAZILIAN DRUG LORD.

08:34.748 --> 08:37.484
HE'S NOW DABBLING IN ARMS.
WHAT KIND OF WEAPONS?

08:37.517 --> 08:39.687
SURFACE-TO-AIR MISSILES.

08:39.720 --> 08:43.023
RUIZ CLAIMS THAT HIS BUDDY IN
BRAZIL GOT HOLD OF A CRATE LOAD.

08:43.056 --> 08:45.425
HE'S ALREADY USED ONE TO DOWN
A DRUG ERADICATION PLANE.

08:45.458 --> 08:47.661
PLANS TO SELL THE REST
TO THE HIGHEST BIDDER.

08:47.695 --> 08:49.930
AND WHO'S THAT?
BETTER BE YOU,

08:49.963 --> 08:53.166
BECAUSE WE HEAR THE ISLAMIC
BRIGADE OF BASRA CITY'S
SNIFFING AROUND DOWN THERE...

08:53.200 --> 08:55.769
FOR SAMs TO
TAKE DOWN OUR BLACK HAWKS.

08:55.803 --> 08:59.673
- MAYBE A CIVILIAN PLANE OR TWO
HERE IN THE U.S.
- IF THEY OUTBID US ON THE SAMs?

08:59.707 --> 09:01.609
WHAT YOU CAN'T BUY,
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO TAKE.

09:01.642 --> 09:05.613
PLANE LEAVES IN AN HOUR.
JONAS AND CHARLIE
ARE ALREADY DOWN THERE.

09:24.564 --> 09:28.035
JIMENEZ HAS FOUR GUARD-TEAMS
ON THE PERIMETER.

09:28.068 --> 09:29.837
AK-47's.

09:32.005 --> 09:34.608
I HATE TO TELL YOU,
BUT THESE ARE ALL KIDS.

09:41.849 --> 09:44.618
OH, BOY.

09:44.652 --> 09:48.288
SOMETHING CATCH YOUR EYE?
JUST SAW AN OLD FRIEND.

09:54.995 --> 09:57.665
THANK YOU.
HAVE A NICE DAY.
THANK YOU. YOU TOO.

09:59.967 --> 10:02.569
THOUGHT YOU'D BE OUT
BUYING T-BONES AND CAVIAR.

10:02.602 --> 10:05.806
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?
MOLLY'S A GENIUS.

10:05.839 --> 10:07.975
WE MADE 10%
ON OUR FIRST INVESTMENT
IN LESS THAN A MONTH.

10:08.008 --> 10:10.410
GOING STRAIGHT INTO
THE KIDS' COLLEGE FUND.

10:10.443 --> 10:12.813
SO WE'RE NOT INVITED
FOR STEAKS?
[ Giggles ]

10:12.846 --> 10:16.483
YOU'RE WELCOME FOR SPAGHETTI.
UNLESS I GET EVICTED.

10:16.516 --> 10:18.418
HAVE YOU SEEN THESE?

10:18.451 --> 10:21.288
IT'S JUST A WARNING.
YOUR FRONT YARD--
WEEDS ARE OVERGROWN.

10:21.321 --> 10:24.424
[ Chuckles ]
NO, REALLY.

10:24.457 --> 10:28.829
CITATION 621-J2.
621'S YOUR YARD.
J2'S WEEDS.

10:28.862 --> 10:31.832
GOTTA GET A WEED WHACKER.
I'D LOAN YOU OURS,
BUT IT BROKE.

10:31.865 --> 10:34.267
OH, COME ON.
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

10:34.301 --> 10:37.270
BRING IT TO
THE F.R.G. MEETING TONIGHT.
YOU CAN APPEAL IT.

10:37.304 --> 10:39.673
I HAVE A PAPER DUE.
SO PAY THE FINE THEN.

10:39.707 --> 10:41.875
WHERE'S THE MEETING?

10:41.909 --> 10:43.643
MY HUSBAND'S CHECK
IS TWO DAYS LATE.

10:43.677 --> 10:45.846
- I'M SORRY.
- IT'S ONLY $20.

10:45.879 --> 10:48.015
I NEED THE MONEY.

10:48.048 --> 10:52.319
- YOUR ACCOUNT IS OVERDRAWN.
- GIVE ME CREDIT FOR THE P.X.
SO THAT I CAN FEED MY SON!

10:52.352 --> 10:54.822
- THERE'S NO CREDIT HERE.
IT'D COST ME MY JOB!
- REC CENTER, 5:00.

10:54.855 --> 10:58.191
ALL I WANT IS WHAT
MY FAMILY IS OWED.

10:58.225 --> 11:00.694
I'M SORRY. IT'S PROCEDURE.
WE'VE BEEN--
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

11:00.728 --> 11:04.197
- THERE A PROBLEM?
- YEAH. YOU LISTENING TO
MY BUSINESS IS A PROBLEM.

11:04.231 --> 11:06.867
JUST NEEDED A LITTLE HELP.

11:06.900 --> 11:09.837
[ Groans ]
ARMY FINANCE SCREWED UP
OUR PAY AGAIN.

11:09.870 --> 11:13.040
I CAN LOAN YOU SOME MONEY
FOR ESSENTIALS.

11:13.073 --> 11:15.675
- I CAN'T LET YOU DO THAT.
- SURE, YOU CAN.
I'M HAVING A GOOD DAY.

11:15.709 --> 11:17.644
WELL, I'M NOT,
AND I DON'T TAKE CHARITY.

11:17.677 --> 11:20.013
IT'S NOT CHARITY
IF YOU PAY ME BACK.
IT'S NOT--

11:22.916 --> 11:25.753
I'M FINE.

11:29.089 --> 11:31.859
SHE'LL GO TO LUCKY LARRY'S,
GET A PAYDAY ADVANCE.

11:34.294 --> 11:36.663
AN ARMY WIFE HAS TO GO TO
A LOAN SHARK TO BUY MILK?

11:36.696 --> 11:39.532
YOU NEW ON BASE?

11:41.401 --> 11:45.773
* [ Drums, Band ]

11:45.806 --> 11:48.809
[ Knocking ]

11:57.417 --> 12:01.354
- NICE FLIGHT?
- IT LANDED.

12:01.388 --> 12:03.791
HAD A FLIGHT ATTENDANT
RIGHT UP YOUR ALLEY.

12:03.824 --> 12:05.959
HOPE YOU PASSED OUT MY NUMBER.
I SURE DID.

12:05.993 --> 12:07.928
HE'S GONNA CALL YOU
WHEN HE GETS BACK
TO THE STATES.

12:07.961 --> 12:10.764
[ Men Chuckle ]
HOPE YOU'RE HUNGRY.

12:10.798 --> 12:13.133
I'M STARVING.
[ Jonas ]
GOOD.

12:13.166 --> 12:16.970
BECAUSE I'M MAKING
CRISTIANOS Y MORROS.

12:17.004 --> 12:20.974
WHOA-HO.
MUCH MORE OF THAT,
YOU MIGHT GET DESSERT TOO.

12:28.315 --> 12:30.317
[ Woman ]
I APOLOGIZE
FOR OUR MEETING'S LENGTH.

12:30.350 --> 12:32.319
I'M AFRAID WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO
PUT OFF OTHER BUSINESS...

12:32.352 --> 12:34.554
AND COMMUNITY COMMENTS
UNTIL THE NEXT TIME,

12:34.587 --> 12:37.757
BECAUSE WE STILL NEED
AN UPDATE WITH THE SIDEWALK
ADDRESS PAINTING...

12:37.791 --> 12:40.327
AND THE RED, WHITE
AND BLUE GARDEN PROJECT.

12:40.360 --> 12:43.263
NOW--
EXCUSE ME.
I DON'T MEAN TO INTERRUPT.

12:43.296 --> 12:46.934
BUT I HAVE SAT HERE
FOR TWO HOURS IN ORDER TO
BRING UP MY OTHER BUSINESS--

12:46.967 --> 12:51.404
PLEASE, PLEASE.
INTRODUCE YOURSELF
AND TELL US YOUR HUSBAND'S RANK.

12:51.438 --> 12:54.808
KIM BROWN. MY HUSBAND BOB
WORKS FOR THE 303rd LOGISTICAL.

12:54.842 --> 12:57.777
HE'S AN N.C.O.

12:57.811 --> 13:00.780
THANK YOU FOR COMING, KIM.
MY NAME IS KATHRYN PRATT.

13:00.814 --> 13:03.016
I AM THE PRESIDENT OF
THE FAMILY READINESS GROUP.

13:03.050 --> 13:05.853
AND MY HUSBAND IS
GENERAL EDWARD PRATT.

13:05.886 --> 13:08.021
PLEASED TO MEET YOU.

13:08.055 --> 13:11.291
I RECEIVED THIS LETTER WHICH
SEEMS TO BE A WARNING THAT
I'LL BE FINED IF MY FRONT YARD--

13:11.324 --> 13:14.794
MY WEEDS-- DON'T MEET
SOME SORT OF STANDARD.

13:14.828 --> 13:18.331
AND I'M NOT SURE TO WHAT
STANDARD IT REFERS.

13:18.365 --> 13:20.934
OUR STEERING COMMITTEE
SETS THE STANDARDS.

13:20.968 --> 13:23.703
YOU ARE NEW TO FORT GRIFFITH?
YES.

13:23.736 --> 13:26.940
PERHAPS YOU FAILED TO READ
THE WIVES' MANUAL
OR EVEN FAILED TO RECEIVE ONE.

13:26.974 --> 13:29.309
MOLLY GAVE ME
THE FULL WELCOME PACKET.

13:29.342 --> 13:31.278
WELL, SHOULD YOU READ IT,
YOU WILL LEARN...

13:31.311 --> 13:34.114
THAT WE DO ENFORCE
COMMUNITY STANDARDS
FOR LAWN UPKEEP,

13:34.147 --> 13:38.518
AND WE RECENTLY
INITIATED THE RED, WHITE
AND BLUE FLOWER PROJECT.

13:38.551 --> 13:41.454
AND BUYING IN BULK, I WAS ABLE
TO PROCURE A DISCOUNT...

13:41.488 --> 13:45.525
SO THAT THE PLANTS
WILL ONLY COME TO $22.

13:45.558 --> 13:48.461
I HAVE NEIGHBORS
GOING TO LOAN SHARKS
TO BUY THEIR GROCERIES.

13:48.495 --> 13:51.164
HOW CAN YOU EXPECT FOLKS
TO SPEND MONEY ON FLOWERS?

13:51.198 --> 13:56.369
WELL, MAYBE YOU HAVE FORGOTTEN
THE IMPORTANCE OF SUCH GESTURES
WITH YOUR HUSBAND NOT IN COMBAT.

13:56.403 --> 14:00.207
I JUST THINK THERE MAY BE
SOME MORE VITAL ISSUES THAT
FAMILY READINESS CAN ADDRESS.

14:00.240 --> 14:02.475
WHY DON'T YOU PUT
YOUR THOUGHTS IN WRITING...

14:02.509 --> 14:05.212
AND BRING THEM
TO THE GENERAL MEETING
ON THURSDAY, KIM?

14:05.245 --> 14:09.182
OH, BUT DON'T DELAY IN
RESPONDING TO THAT 621-J2,

14:09.216 --> 14:12.986
AS THERE IS AN ADDED FINE
FOR A LATE PAYMENT.

14:13.020 --> 14:15.155
SO, MOVING ON.

14:15.188 --> 14:20.994
NOW EACH FLAT HERE IS
PREARRANGED IN RED AND WHITE
IMPATIENS AND BLUE LOBELIA.

14:21.028 --> 14:24.898
I WANTED TO TELL HER
MY HUSBAND'S ONE OF THE TOP 150
ELITE SOLDIERS IN THE WORLD...

14:24.932 --> 14:26.866
AND THEN PUNCH HER
RIGHT IN THE THROAT.

14:26.900 --> 14:30.837
- YOU MADE A POINT ABOUT
NEEDY FAMILIES ON THE BASE.
- OH, YOU THINK SO?

14:30.870 --> 14:35.208
BUT YOU CAN'T BARGE IN AND
TURN AN OLD, STUFFY INSTITUTION
AROUND ON A DIME.

14:35.242 --> 14:37.144
BUT YOU'RE SMART.
PERHAPS YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

14:38.611 --> 14:40.847
WHAT'S THAT?

14:40.880 --> 14:45.618
WRITING US OFF.
MAKING SURE THE F.R.G.
IS A WASTE OF YOUR TIME.

14:45.652 --> 14:49.589
OTHERWISE, YOU MIGHT HAVE
TO ROLL UP YOUR SLEEVES
AND GET YOUR HANDS DIRTY.

15:14.814 --> 15:17.250
GRAB YOUR PARTNER.
BAND JUST STARTED PLAYING.

15:22.355 --> 15:25.125
[ Shouting In Portuguese ]

15:28.761 --> 15:31.164
WE'RE HERE TO
SEE ADOLPHO JIMENEZ.

15:31.198 --> 15:33.766
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

15:33.800 --> 15:35.969
ANYONE HERE SPEAK ENGLISH?

15:36.003 --> 15:37.971
I DO. HE ASKED
WHO YOU WERE.

15:38.005 --> 15:40.907
TELL HIM WE'RE HERE TO DO
BUSINESS WITH YOUR BOSS.

15:40.940 --> 15:42.475
[ Boy Speaks Portuguese ]

15:53.186 --> 15:55.622
TELL HIM WE'RE FRIENDS
OF RICARDO RUIZ.

16:09.669 --> 16:11.904
[ Cheering ]

16:24.651 --> 16:26.519
MR. JIMENEZ?

16:35.095 --> 16:37.897
MR. JIMENEZ, MY NAME
IS LIAM HIGGINS.

16:37.930 --> 16:40.133
THIS IS OWEN DONNELLY.

16:40.167 --> 16:43.803
WE REPRESENT A CERTAIN
IRISH-AMERICAN CONSTITUENCY.

16:43.836 --> 16:47.140
- WE'RE LOOKING FOR A FRIEND.
- AND WHO MIGHT THAT BE?

16:47.174 --> 16:49.376
HE CALLS HIMSELF SAM.

16:49.409 --> 16:52.145
WE UNDERSTAND YOU MIGHT
BE OF SOME ASSISTANCE.

16:52.179 --> 16:54.881
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?

16:54.914 --> 16:57.917
WELL, YOU WOULD BE
WELL COMPENSATED.

16:57.950 --> 17:00.220
WHO ARE YOU? I.R.A.?

17:01.521 --> 17:03.590
I THOUGHT YOU MADE PEACE
WITH THE BRITISH.

17:03.623 --> 17:06.159
WE'RE NOT I.R.A.

17:06.193 --> 17:09.162
[ Irish Accent ]
YOU WOULDN'T CATCH US SIGNING
A BLEEDING PEACE TREATY...

17:09.196 --> 17:11.398
WHEN THERE'S
STILL A WAR ON.

17:11.431 --> 17:13.400
DOES IT MATTER WHO WE ARE?
WE HAVE THE MONEY.

17:13.433 --> 17:18.238
$500,000.
THE OTHER FIVE UPON DELIVERY.

17:19.806 --> 17:21.774
FOR HOW MANY SAMs?

17:21.808 --> 17:23.776
FOR ALL OF THEM.

17:28.548 --> 17:30.450
HOW DID YOU FIND ME?

17:30.483 --> 17:32.552
WE HAVE A MUTUAL FRIEND--
RICARDO RUIZ.

17:36.156 --> 17:38.725
AND WHEN DID HE
TELL YOU ABOUT ME?

17:38.758 --> 17:41.894
I SPOKE TO HIM TWO DAYS AGO.
YOU FAILED TO
DO YOUR HOMEWORK.

17:41.928 --> 17:46.032
RICARDO DIED LAST WEEK.

17:46.065 --> 17:48.301
- EH--
- I'LL KILL HIM.

17:48.335 --> 17:51.804
GO AHEAD.
THERE'S A THOUSAND OTHERS
TO FILL HIS SHOES.

17:51.838 --> 17:53.973
HOLD IT.
WAIT. HOLD ON.

17:54.006 --> 17:56.243
EH, EH.
LOOK AT THIS.

17:59.479 --> 18:02.349
[ Man Grunts ]

18:04.617 --> 18:07.420
YOU'LL NOTE THE NEWSPAPER'S
TWO DAYS OLD.

18:07.454 --> 18:09.489
YOU THINK I DON'T KNOW
PICTURES CAN BE FAKED?

18:09.522 --> 18:14.093
RICARDO FAKED HIS OWN DEATH
TO AVOID SOME PROBLEMS HE WAS
HAVING WITH THE SALVADORANS.

18:14.127 --> 18:17.164
YOU MEAN WITH THE BOLIVIANS.
NO. HE PAID OFF MR. BONITA.

18:17.197 --> 18:19.799
IT WAS MR. ALERIA
IN EL SALVADOR WHO
WAS GROWING IMPATIENT.

18:22.969 --> 18:25.305
I CAN GET RUIZ
ON THE PHONE RIGHT NOW.

18:38.818 --> 18:41.654
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

18:53.700 --> 18:55.702
[ Closes Cell Phone ]

19:03.510 --> 19:06.179
[ Sighs ]

19:19.192 --> 19:22.028
YOU SENSED I WOULD NOT SHOOT
ONE OF MY BOYS.

19:22.061 --> 19:25.298
I'VE GROWN TOO FOND OF THEM.

19:25.332 --> 19:29.302
I ADMIT, IT'S A WEAKNESS
I MUST CORRECT ONE DAY.

19:29.336 --> 19:33.673
RICARDO SAYS YOU ARE
A MAN OF YOUR WORD.

19:33.706 --> 19:36.175
[ Irish Accent ]
THEN SHOW US
THE BLOODY ROCKETS.

19:56.263 --> 19:58.197
THESE AREN'T JUST ANY SAMs.

19:59.732 --> 20:03.903
THESE ARE STINGERS.
AS THEY SAY, MADE IN AMERICA.

20:03.936 --> 20:07.640
- WE'LL TAKE ALL SEVEN.
- NOT SO FAST.

20:09.276 --> 20:12.512
- THERE ARE OTHER BIDDERS.
- WHO?

20:12.545 --> 20:15.682
MEN, SUCH AS YOURSELF,
WHO ALSO DO NOT LIKE
AN OCCUPYING ARMY ON THEIR LAND.

20:15.715 --> 20:17.750
WE'LL TAKE THEM ALL.

20:17.784 --> 20:21.187
RICARDO'S WORD
GOT YOU A LOOK,
NOT A SALE.

20:21.220 --> 20:22.922
WITH COMPETITORS,
THE PRICE HAS GONE UP.

20:22.955 --> 20:26.593
[ Sighs ]
HOW MUCH?

20:26.626 --> 20:30.196
TWO MILLION FOR THE SEVEN.
I'D HAVE TO MAKE A CALL.

20:30.229 --> 20:32.465
MAKE YOUR CALL.
I'M SURE
IN A COUPLE OF DAYS--

20:32.499 --> 20:34.567
YOU HAVE UNTIL TOMORROW.

20:40.440 --> 20:42.975
[ Phone Rings ]

20:44.277 --> 20:46.513
[ Man ]
COLONEL RYAN?

20:48.781 --> 20:50.950
RYAN.

20:50.983 --> 20:53.553
WE CAN CONFIRM THEY HAVE
THE DRESS IN YOUR WIFE'S SIZE...

20:53.586 --> 20:56.122
- BUT WE'RE GONNA NEED
SOME MORE BUTTONS.
- HOW MANY BUTTONS?

20:56.155 --> 20:59.626
DOUBLE THE ORIGINAL AMOUNT.
COPY THAT IF I HAVE
A COUPLE WEEKS.

20:59.659 --> 21:02.462
NEGATIVE. FASHION SHOW
STARTS TOMORROW.

21:02.495 --> 21:05.898
MY INVESTORS WON'T AUTHORIZE
ANY MORE BUTTONS GOING TO
THAT PARTICULAR SUPPLIER.

21:05.932 --> 21:08.901
UNDERSTOOD.
BUT THERE ARE COMPLICATIONS.

21:08.935 --> 21:10.837
WHICH ARE?

21:10.870 --> 21:13.540
A LOT OF CHILD LABOR
IN THE FACTORY.

21:15.508 --> 21:17.810
CLOSE THE TRANSACTION,
CHILD LABOR OR NOT.

21:17.844 --> 21:19.946
ROGER.

21:34.126 --> 21:37.730
WE'RE TO OBTAIN THE STINGERS
IF NOT WITH MONEY,
THEN BY FORCE.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.835
THAT'S A LOT OF KIDS
TO GO THROUGH.

21:44.904 --> 21:50.209
ANYONE HAS ANY IDEAS OF
HOW TO GO AROUND THEM INSTEAD,
CLOCK'S TICKING.

21:59.986 --> 22:02.889
HERE YOU GO.
YOUR FIRST REAL ESTATE PROFIT.

22:02.922 --> 22:05.458
$400 FREE AND CLEAR.

22:05.492 --> 22:08.361
AND THE OTHER HALF
GOES BACK INTO THE KITTY?

22:08.395 --> 22:11.964
FOR OUR CLUB'S NEXT PURCHASE.
THERE'S A WAREHOUSE ON THE
INTERSTATE I'VE GOT MY EYE ON.

22:11.998 --> 22:15.067
- MAYBE WE SHOULD BUY OUT
LUCKY LARRY.
- GOOD WAY TO LOSE OUR SOULS.

22:15.101 --> 22:19.138
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT
WHAT YOU SAID. AND I'VE BEEN
CHECKING OUT THESE LOAN SHARKS.

22:19.171 --> 22:22.241
THIRTY-FIVE PERCENT INTEREST
THEY CHARGE THESE POOR WOMEN.

22:22.274 --> 22:25.545
AFTER 60 DAYS IT GOES TO 40.
I'VE BEEN THERE.

22:25.578 --> 22:28.981
AND THEY CONTACT
YOUR SUPERIOR OFFICER
IF YOU DEFAULT.

22:29.015 --> 22:31.418
IS THAT LEGAL?
ARMY FROWNS ON DEBT.

22:31.451 --> 22:35.054
BUT THE F.R.G. COULD HELP.
LIKE WITH OUR INVESTMENT CLUB.

22:35.087 --> 22:38.891
WE COULD POOL RESOURCES.
INSTEAD OF BUYING FLOWERS,
WE COULD HAVE DUES.

22:38.925 --> 22:41.761
OR EVEN USE SOME OF
THE INVESTMENT CLUB'S KITTY
AS SEED MONEY.

22:41.794 --> 22:43.763
BILL GATES DIDN'T
GET PHILANTHROPIC
HIS FIRST QUARTER.

22:43.796 --> 22:46.933
I'M JUST SAYIN'.
ACCORDING TO
THE F.R.G. HANDBOOK--

22:46.966 --> 22:49.201
OH, YOU FOUND
YOUR WELCOME PACKET,
DID YOU?

22:49.235 --> 22:52.672
THERE IS NOTHING IN THE BYLAWS
TO PREVENT THE F.R.G.
FROM PROVIDING A SAFETY NET.

22:52.705 --> 22:55.341
I LOOK FORWARD TO YOU
SELLING KATHRYN ON THIS.

22:55.374 --> 22:57.777
NOTHING IN THE BYLAWS TO
PREVENT A REGIME CHANGE EITHER.

22:57.810 --> 23:01.180
WELL, I DID
LAY DOWN THE GAUNTLET.
MOLLY, IF I GET INVOLVED--

23:01.213 --> 23:04.283
I MEAN, I'M NEW HERE.
NOBODY KNOWS ME.

23:04.316 --> 23:07.787
AND IF I GET THINGS ROLLING,
CAN I COUNT YOU IN?

23:11.090 --> 23:13.159
I'M NOT OPPOSED
TO NEW IDEAS.

23:17.296 --> 23:20.700
[ Man ]
TOM!
ADDEUS!

23:20.733 --> 23:23.903
DAMN, IT'S GOOD TO
SEE YOU! WHAT THE HELL
BRINGS YOU DOWN HERE?

23:23.936 --> 23:27.306
WELL, LET'S TALK.
COME ON IN.
SIT DOWN.

23:30.843 --> 23:33.045
HOW'S THE FAMILY?

23:33.079 --> 23:36.783
WELL, THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.
LAURENDA.

23:36.816 --> 23:39.886
HOW IS LAURENDA?
SHE'S GETTING SERIOUS
ABOUT A SOLDIER.

23:39.919 --> 23:42.655
ABOUT A SOLDIER?
WAIT A MINUTE.
SHE'S-- SHE'S HOW OLD?

23:42.689 --> 23:46.826
- TWENTY-THREE, TOM.
- WHERE DOES IT GO?

23:46.859 --> 23:49.061
WHAT'S SO BAD
ABOUT A SOLDIER?

23:49.095 --> 23:53.132
WELL, THE PROBLEM IS
THE MAN THAT MY LAURENDA'S
SO FOND OF LACKS AMBITION.

23:53.165 --> 23:56.135
I'M TRYING TO GET HIM
OUT OF A CUBICLE
AND INTO THE 82nd.

23:56.168 --> 23:59.338
IT'S DONE.
WHAT'S HIS NAME?

23:59.371 --> 24:01.440
HECTOR WILLIAMS.

24:03.042 --> 24:05.077
I HAVE ASKED ALL
UP AND DOWN THE BASE.

24:05.111 --> 24:07.113
CAN'T FIND A DAMN THING OUT
ABOUT THE BOY.

24:07.146 --> 24:09.949
I MEAN, HE MUST BE BURIED
IN A BASEMENT SOMEWHERE
WITH THE FILING CABINETS.

24:11.350 --> 24:13.753
NEED YOU TO STAND DOWN,
ADDEUS.

24:13.786 --> 24:17.790
STAND DOWN?
NO MORE QUESTIONS
ABOUT WILLIAMS. WE CLEAR?

24:17.824 --> 24:20.660
YOU SAYIN'--

24:20.693 --> 24:23.162
I'M SAYING YOU NEED
TO STAND DOWN.

24:23.195 --> 24:25.998
REALLY?

24:27.199 --> 24:29.235
REALLY.

24:34.974 --> 24:38.177
[ Popping ]

24:38.210 --> 24:40.780
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

24:40.813 --> 24:42.615
[ Popping ]

24:42.649 --> 24:44.483
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

24:45.985 --> 24:50.189
[ Shouting In Portuguese ]

24:52.559 --> 24:57.163
[ Shouting Continues ]

25:02.268 --> 25:04.503
[ Continues In Portuguese ]

25:17.550 --> 25:19.518
[ Popping In Distance ]

25:36.102 --> 25:40.640
[ Shouts In Portuguese ]

25:42.575 --> 25:44.877
[ Speaking Portuguese ]

25:53.385 --> 25:55.655
[ Popping Continues ]

26:13.606 --> 26:15.474
[ Speaks Portuguese ]

26:27.820 --> 26:30.489
I SEE ONE.

26:31.523 --> 26:33.726
THERE WERE SEVEN.

26:33.760 --> 26:36.128
[ Sighs ]
WE'RE MISSING SIX?

26:38.264 --> 26:41.133
- HOW'S THE FIREWORKS SHOW
HOLDING UP?
- WE'RE ON OUR LAST FEW.

26:41.167 --> 26:43.102
MAKE 'EM LAST.
WE NEED MORE TIME.

26:43.135 --> 26:45.471
YOU'RE ABOUT TO HEAR
THE REAL THING, BOSS.
WE GOT VISITORS.

26:45.504 --> 26:46.673
ROGER THAT.

26:56.148 --> 26:58.685
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

27:02.054 --> 27:04.023
CALL OFF YOUR SOLDIERS.

27:04.056 --> 27:06.358
TELL THEM
THEY'RE JUST FIREWORKS.

27:06.392 --> 27:09.662
AND THEN TELL THEM
TO GO HOME... NOW.

27:11.363 --> 27:15.001
[ Shouts In Portuguese ]

27:20.840 --> 27:24.476
[ Continues Shouting ]

27:29.181 --> 27:31.583
NOW CLOSE THE DOOR.

27:42.762 --> 27:47.033
TWO NOSTRILS,
TWO EARS, TWO EYES.

27:48.367 --> 27:50.402
WE CLEAR
WHO'S IN CHARGE HERE?

27:50.436 --> 27:52.404
YES.

27:52.438 --> 27:54.540
WHERE ARE THE STINGERS?
I KEPT ONE.

27:54.573 --> 27:56.542
AND THE REST?
I SOLD THEM.

27:56.575 --> 27:59.311
- TO WHO?
- THE ISLAMIC BRIGADE.

27:59.345 --> 28:01.313
HOW LONG AGO?
FORTY MINUTES.

28:01.347 --> 28:05.017
WHERE ARE THEY TAKING THEM?
OUT OF THE COUNTRY.

28:05.051 --> 28:07.920
- FROM WHERE?
- I-I DON'T KNOW.

28:09.856 --> 28:11.357
[ Grunts ]

28:11.390 --> 28:14.693
FROM WHERE?
I DON'T KNOW.

28:14.727 --> 28:19.899
I JUST KNOW THEY ARE GOING
TO SNEAK THEM INTO AMERICA...
TO SHOOT DOWN PLANES...

28:19.932 --> 28:21.600
FOR PASSENGER FLIGHTS.

28:23.870 --> 28:27.273
YOU HAVE TWO CHILDREN IN
A BOARDING SCHOOL IN LONDON.

28:28.274 --> 28:31.143
THIS LOOK LIKE THEM?

28:32.444 --> 28:36.548
IF I EVER HEAR OF YOU
SELLING WEAPONS AGAIN,

28:36.582 --> 28:38.885
I WILL BRING YOU
THEIR SEVERED HEADS...

28:38.918 --> 28:41.187
AND THAT WILL BE
THE LAST THING
YOU SEE IN THIS LIFE.

28:41.220 --> 28:43.555
YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

28:45.992 --> 28:49.862
YOU DEAF,
OR YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

28:49.896 --> 28:52.131
I UNDERSTAND.

29:18.757 --> 29:21.961
TOOK A FEW PRISONERS.
WHERE ARE THE OTHER STINGERS?

29:21.994 --> 29:24.797
OUT OF OUR CONTROL.
THAT'S NOT GOOD.

29:28.835 --> 29:31.070
THIS IS SNAKE DOCTOR.

29:31.103 --> 29:35.074
FROM MY LOCATION, GIVE ME
THE DISTANCE AND DIRECTION
OF THE FIVE NEAREST AIRFIELDS.

29:35.107 --> 29:37.076
SEND.

29:37.109 --> 29:39.078
[ Beeps ]

29:39.111 --> 29:41.113
ROGER, OUT.

29:46.385 --> 29:50.156
BIG TURNOUT.
[ Kathryn ]
LADIES? LADIES, PLEASE.

29:50.189 --> 29:52.324
THIS MEETING NEEDS
TO BE CALLED TO ORDER.

29:52.358 --> 29:55.661
COME ON. LET'S START.
WE NEED TO GET GOING.

29:57.864 --> 30:02.034
"MOLLY BLANE WILL TURN
FAMILY READINESS
INTO FAMILY RESPONSIBILITY?"

30:02.068 --> 30:04.003
GIRL DOESN'T KNOW WHAT
SHE'S GOTTEN HERSELF INTO.

30:04.036 --> 30:07.606
MOLLY!
MOLLY! MOLLY!

30:07.639 --> 30:10.776
[ Ladies Chanting ]

30:10.809 --> 30:13.812
LADIES, ORDER.
ORDER.

30:13.846 --> 30:18.117
ORDER. I AM PLEASED
TO SEE SO MANY
NEW MEMBERS HERE.

30:18.150 --> 30:23.055
AND PER THE F.R.G. BYLAWS,
THE GENERAL MEMBERSHIP HAS
THE RIGHT, AT THEIR DISCRETION,

30:23.089 --> 30:25.191
TO CALL AN ELECTION
FOR NEW OFFICERS.

30:25.224 --> 30:27.226
ARTICLE 3, SECTION 2.

30:27.259 --> 30:33.165
THAT'S TRUE. AND
THE CURRENT OFFICERS ARE EAGER
TO HEAR ALL MEMBER CONCERNS.

30:33.199 --> 30:38.204
BUT FIRST, I WANT TO REPORT ON
THE STATUS OF THE RED, WHITE
AND BLUE HOME GARDEN PROJECT...

30:38.237 --> 30:44.210
WHICH YOU MAY NOT HAVE HEARD OF.
NO ONE CARES ABOUT PLANTS.
WE BARELY HAVE MONEY FOR FOOD.

30:44.243 --> 30:46.212
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.
GET RID OF THOSE
LOAN SHARKS.

30:46.245 --> 30:49.048
YEAH. TELL US HOW
THE F.R.G. IS GOING TO
GIVE US SHORT-TERM LOANS.

30:49.081 --> 30:53.085
WHAT ABOUT MORE JOBS
ON BASE FOR US WIVES?
WHY NOT DO SOMETHING ABOUT THAT?

30:53.119 --> 30:55.487
SPOUSE EMPLOYMENT IS HANDLED
BY ANOTHER COM--

30:55.521 --> 30:59.191
IT ISN'T JUST THE LOAN SHARKS
PREYING ON US. IT MIGHT NOT
MATTER TO OFFICERS' WIVES--

30:59.225 --> 31:02.094
LADIES, KATHRYN'S TRYING
TO EXPLAIN--

31:02.128 --> 31:04.096
I SAY LET'S VOTE.
I SECOND THE MOTION.

31:04.130 --> 31:06.765
[ Applause ]

31:18.077 --> 31:22.114
IF THEY HAVE WHEELS,
THEY COULD'VE ALREADY
FOUND AN AIRFIELD.

31:22.148 --> 31:25.051
THAT CASE,
THOSE ROCKETS ARE GONE.

31:27.886 --> 31:31.924
[ Speaks Portuguese ]

31:36.562 --> 31:39.198
[ Spits ]

31:39.231 --> 31:45.171
[ Speaks Portuguese ]

31:47.006 --> 31:49.441
[ Continues In Portuguese ]

31:51.277 --> 31:54.646
- YOU.
- UNTIE ME.
I'M NOT A DOG.

31:57.849 --> 32:00.119
- GET UP.
- HELP US.

32:00.152 --> 32:02.154
NO.
OR YOU'LL GET A BEATING.

32:02.188 --> 32:04.423
LET ME GO BACK.
THEY'LL SUSPECT ME.

32:04.456 --> 32:06.625
YOU'LL GO BACK WHEN YOU TELL ME
EVERYTHING I NEED TO KNOW.

32:06.658 --> 32:10.262
THIS CONVERSATION HAS NO MEANING
IF THOSE MEN AND THOSE ROCKETS
HAVE GONE. YOU UNDERSTAND?

32:10.296 --> 32:13.299
THEY ARE NOT GONE.
YOU SURE?

32:13.332 --> 32:15.301
I KNOW WHERE THEY'RE GOING.
SHOW ME.

32:15.334 --> 32:18.504
NO! NO!

32:20.172 --> 32:22.841
THEN TELL ME.

32:22.874 --> 32:24.943
TAKE ME TO AMERICA.

32:28.114 --> 32:30.082
ALL RIGHT.

32:30.116 --> 32:33.019
SWEAR IT?

32:33.052 --> 32:37.223
I SWEAR I WILL
TAKE YOU TO AMERICA WHEN
WE'RE DONE WITH THIS.

32:39.891 --> 32:42.661
THE MEN HAVE
A HELICOPTER CLOSE BY.

32:44.696 --> 32:48.200
FACE ME.
I'M GONNA PULL MY ARM BACK
AS IF I'M GONNA HIT YOU.

32:48.234 --> 32:51.670
WHEN I BRING MY ARM FORWARD,
YOU SCREAM AND DROP.

32:52.804 --> 32:55.541
[ Grunts ]

32:57.009 --> 32:58.977
UNTIE THEM.
UNTIE THEM ALL.

32:59.011 --> 33:01.680
THEY'RE USELESS.

33:01.713 --> 33:05.417
[ Sighs ]

33:09.588 --> 33:12.491
COLONEL.
YOU'RE UP EARLY.

33:12.524 --> 33:15.061
I HEARD YOU GOT YOURSELF
ELECTED TO ANOTHER JOB.

33:15.094 --> 33:17.229
ONE I REFUSED TO ACCEPT.

33:17.263 --> 33:20.832
DID KATHRYN PRATT MENTION THAT
WHEN SHE CALLED TO COMPLAIN?

33:20.866 --> 33:23.735
KATHRYN DIDN'T
PLACE THE CALL. GENERAL PRATT
DID THAT ALL BY HIMSELF.

33:23.769 --> 33:27.039
THE MISSUS WAS WHISPERING
IN HIS EAR
IN THE BACKGROUND.

33:27.073 --> 33:30.576
THIS IS THE THIRD TIME
I'VE BEEN ALERTED TO KIM BROWN.

33:30.609 --> 33:34.813
SHE'S A RUNAWAY PONY. YOU PUT
A SNAFFLE BIT ON HER BEFORE
SHE BRINGS THE WHOLE THING DOWN.

33:34.846 --> 33:37.849
SHE DIDN'T MEAN TO.
GENERAL PRATT IS
HELPING RUN A WAR.

33:37.883 --> 33:41.720
- HE DOESN'T HAVE TIME
TO GO AFTER LUCKY LARRY.
- LUCKY LARRY?

33:41.753 --> 33:44.690
HIS WIFE'S
ALL OVER HIS ASS ABOUT LOAN
SHARKS PREYING ON THE WIVES.

33:44.723 --> 33:47.025
IS SHE?

33:47.059 --> 33:49.995
KIM'S GOT HER ALL FIRED UP
ABOUT SPOUSES GETTING THEIR
HUSBANDS' CHECKS LATE...

33:50.028 --> 33:52.764
AND NEEDING CREDIT
AT THE COMMISSARY
AND OTHER BUSINESSES.

33:52.798 --> 33:56.702
- KATHRYN PRATT'S FIRED UP?
- PUT A LID ON THIS, MOLLY.

33:56.735 --> 34:00.206
SORRY, COLONEL.
THIS ONE MAY HAVE
GOTTEN OVER MY HEAD.

34:01.473 --> 34:04.976
I'LL TAKE A RAIN CHECK.

34:14.420 --> 34:17.889
THAT WAY.
THERE.

34:32.771 --> 34:35.974
YUP.
THEY GOT 'EM, BOSS.

34:36.007 --> 34:40.779
- BROWN, CAN YOU HIT IT?
- OH, I BELIEVE SO.

34:40.812 --> 34:42.514
THEN DO IT.

34:57.196 --> 34:58.664
[ Beeping ]
I GOT A LOCK.

34:58.697 --> 35:00.666
COME HERE.

35:17.048 --> 35:19.151
YEAH, IT'S OKAY.

35:19.185 --> 35:21.220
IT'S OVER NOW.

35:40.472 --> 35:43.442
MIAMI. I WANT TO
LIVE IN MIAMI.

35:43.475 --> 35:46.178
I SAW A SHOW ABOUT BRAZILIANS
THAT MOVE TO MIAMI.

35:46.212 --> 35:49.047
IS IT AS PRETTY
AS IT LOOKS?

35:53.319 --> 35:56.588
IT DOESN'T HAVE TO BE MIAMI.
NEW YORK, CHICAGO.

36:14.773 --> 36:17.209
[ Sighs ]

36:30.856 --> 36:33.859
YOU SWORE TO ME!
YOU LIAR!

36:33.892 --> 36:37.863
WHY ARE YOU SUCH A LIAR?
WHY? I HATE YOU! I HATE YOU!
I HATE YOU!

36:37.896 --> 36:41.132
YOU SWORE TO ME!
YOU SWORE TO ME!
YOU SWORE TO ME!

36:42.100 --> 36:45.437
LIAR! LIAR! LIAR!

36:45.471 --> 36:49.275
LET ME GO!

36:50.609 --> 36:54.045
I'M SORRY.
I CAN'T DO IT.
[ Crying ]

36:54.980 --> 36:57.048
[ Kisses ]

36:58.317 --> 37:00.386
[ Sniffs ]

37:15.066 --> 37:17.969
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, HONEY.
YOU WANT THEM IN STRIPES.
RED AND WHITE STRIPES.

37:18.003 --> 37:20.138
YOU DON'T THINK
IT'D LOOK BETTER ALL MIXED UP?

37:20.171 --> 37:23.575
WELL, I THINK IT'D BE
MORE LIKE THE FLAG.
DON'T YOU THINK, MOLLY?

37:23.609 --> 37:25.944
I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

37:25.977 --> 37:28.480
PUNISHING KIM'S
INSUBORDINATION BY
HELPING HER PLANT THESE.

37:28.514 --> 37:31.483
KATHRYN BROUGHT ME
THESE FLOWERS.

37:31.517 --> 37:34.085
EVEN THOUGH IT SHOULD'VE
BEEN ME THANKING HER.

37:34.119 --> 37:36.254
YOU AGREED TO STAY ON
AS PRESIDENT?

37:36.288 --> 37:39.224
WELL, ACTING PRESIDENT, UNTIL
THERE CAN BE A PROPER ELECTION.

37:39.257 --> 37:42.328
ONCE WORD GETS AROUND ABOUT
LUCKY LARRY'S RUN-IN
WITH THE FIRE MARSHAL,

37:42.361 --> 37:44.396
I'M BETTING
KAT'LL BE A SHOO-IN.

37:44.430 --> 37:47.466
KAT?
I'M THE ONE IN DEBT.

37:47.499 --> 37:52.103
KIM REALLY SHOOK US UP,
DIDN'T SHE, MOLLY?
SHE DID INDEED.

37:54.105 --> 37:58.109
[ Laughing ]
I SAID, "NO, CAPTAIN.

37:58.143 --> 38:00.979
"THE WORST THING THAT
A RACIST CAN CALL
AN AFRICAN-AMERICAN...

38:01.012 --> 38:04.149
THAT STARTS WITH 'N'
AND ENDS WITH 'R' IS NEIGHBOR."

38:04.182 --> 38:06.852
[ Laughs ]

38:08.654 --> 38:12.157
A FRIEND OF MINE
GAVE ME TICKETS,
50-YARD LINE.

38:12.190 --> 38:15.527
- WOULD YOU LIKE TO
JOIN ME, SON?
- YES, SIR. THANK YOU. I WOULD.

38:15.561 --> 38:18.464
HOW'D THAT JOB OF YOURS
END UP GOING?

38:18.497 --> 38:21.633
THE ONE THAT TOOK YOU AWAY FROM
HERE SO QUICK YOUR LAST VISIT?

38:21.667 --> 38:25.537
OH. GONE FINE.

38:25.571 --> 38:29.307
WELL, WE ALL DO OUR PART.

38:47.192 --> 38:50.161
* [ Soft Jazz ]

38:50.195 --> 38:52.831
WHAT'S GOING ON?

38:55.567 --> 38:58.670
THAT'S WHAT
I'M ASKING YOU, HECTOR.

38:58.704 --> 39:01.707
MY FATHER DOESN'T JUST
CHANGE ON A DIME LIKE THAT
UNLESS THERE'S A REASON.

39:01.740 --> 39:06.244
THE WAY HE'S ACTING,
YOU'RE NELSON MANDELA
HERE TO SAY GRACE.

39:08.246 --> 39:11.383
YOU WANT TO TELL ME WHY?

39:11.417 --> 39:14.486
- IT'S COMPLICATED.
- THE TRUTH ISN'T COMPLICATED.

39:14.520 --> 39:17.088
WHY ARE YOU MAKING IT
COMPLICATED?

39:17.122 --> 39:20.526
HECTOR,
WHY DON'T YOU COME INSIDE
WITH ME AND HAVE A BRANDY?

39:20.559 --> 39:24.430
- DADDY, I'M TALKING TO HECTOR!
- TALKING HIM TO DEATH
IS MORE LIKE IT.

39:24.463 --> 39:26.865
DADDY, DO YOU WANT TO TELL ME
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

39:26.898 --> 39:30.769
- YOUNG LADY, YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO THIS MAN IS.
- LAURENDA--

39:36.908 --> 39:39.077
THERE ARE SOME PEOPLE
I'D LIKE YOU TO MEET.

39:39.110 --> 39:43.515
WHO ARE THESE PEOPLE?
AND WOULD SOMEONE TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON RIGHT NOW?

39:43.549 --> 39:47.252
I KNEW THAT
THAT GIRL HAD SENSE.

39:47.285 --> 39:51.423
IS THAT WHAT SHE HAS NOW?
IN THIS INSTANCE, YES.
YES, SHE HAS.

39:53.124 --> 39:55.927
SPECIAL FORCES?

39:55.961 --> 40:00.298
FIRST OF ALL,
YOU MISREPRESENTED YOURSELF.
LAURENDA--

40:00.331 --> 40:05.370
AND-AND-- AND I KNOW
YOU WOULD SAY IT'S
FOR REASONS OF SECURITY.

40:05.403 --> 40:10.476
THE WAY I SEE IT,
CALL IT A FIB OR A LIE,
I DON'T LIKE IT.

40:10.509 --> 40:15.447
AND SECOND-- WAIT A SECOND.
SECONDLY, THE MAN I THOUGHT
I WAS FALLING FOR...

40:15.481 --> 40:21.286
WAS IN SOME
NONCOMBATANT SPECIALTY
HE CALLED LOGISTICS.

40:21.319 --> 40:25.924
AND FOOL THAT I WAS,
I SAW SOME PROFESSION
AFTER THE ARMY.

40:28.660 --> 40:32.698
[ Chuckles ]
YOU GONNA TELL ME WHAT-WHAT--
WHAT EMPLOYMENT THERE IS--

40:34.466 --> 40:39.137
A MARRIED MAN LOOKING FOR WORK
PUTS ON HIS RÉSUME "GUNFIGHTER."

40:39.170 --> 40:42.007
LAURENDA--
WELL, THAT'S THE END OF
THIS CONVERSATION.

40:44.275 --> 40:47.513
IT'S BEEN INSTRUCTIVE
KNOWING YOU.

40:47.546 --> 40:50.849
DADDY, YOU SHOW THIS BOY OUT.

40:59.224 --> 41:01.993
- WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO NOW?
- YOU COULD TRY BEGGING.

41:02.027 --> 41:03.995
BEGGING FOR WHAT?
WELL, FOR UNDERSTANDING.

41:04.029 --> 41:07.799
NOTHING TO UNDERSTAND.
SHE'S GOT HER LIFE,
AND SHE DON'T WANT MINE.

41:12.137 --> 41:14.840
THAT FLIGHT ATTENDANT CALL YET?

41:14.873 --> 41:17.308
YEAH. WANTS TO KNOW
IF I THINK YOU LIKE HIM.

41:17.342 --> 41:19.511
[ Chuckles ]

41:19.545 --> 41:23.915
BOSS, HOW'S A UNIT MAN KNOW
WHEN HIS GIRL'S THE RIGHT ONE?

41:26.084 --> 41:29.120
WELL, LIKE THEY SAY,
SEE HER SIDE OF THE ARGUMENT.

41:29.154 --> 41:31.657
ARGUMENT'S OVER.
NO, IT'S NOT. NO.

41:31.690 --> 41:34.960
IT'S NOT.
WHAT'S HER HIDDEN FEAR?
ALL RIGHT?

41:34.993 --> 41:37.629
CHILDREN. HER--

41:37.663 --> 41:41.299
SHE MAY NOT EVEN
KNOW IT HERSELF.
BUT HER CONCERN IS CHILDREN.

41:41.332 --> 41:44.369
THE LIVES OF THE CHILDREN.
AND TO HER CREDIT, THERE IS--

41:44.402 --> 41:48.574
THERE IS NO HIGHER CONCERN--
WOULD YOU LET A MAN
DRINK IN PEACE?

41:52.611 --> 41:56.915
WOULD YOU LET ME
DRINK IN PEACE?

41:56.948 --> 42:01.887
* [ Country ]

